ore":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T05:55:12.000Z","msg":"又搵後生仔黎搞，呢個世代既後生仔真係慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd299986bbf61d640f69218e35f5e06969c6efb8","tid":220454,"uid":60877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T05:57:27.000Z","msg":"講左成個月仲味打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7712e6c81c9ae91d20e9226402026e8a19d2f30","tid":220454,"uid":36600,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T05:58:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pbaj6x9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fpbaj6x9.jpg&h=64e65db7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n朝鮮航母"},{"pid":"8ea8d6e5a847180e33f6a9162e498d2d8adebf61","tid":220454,"uid":23077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T06:00:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pbaj6x9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fpbaj6x9.jpg&h=64e65db7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n朝鮮航母</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  美帝個啲級數都唔夠佢黎"},{"pid":"037c2719b01cf02bbc29fc5f38a9654e49681a24","tid":220454,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T06:01:01.000Z","msg":"dirty bomb"},{"pid":"8ed1820ada48e89c678f6cf44340dbca71d0a28a","tid":220454,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T06:02:13.000Z","msg":"髒彈又叫骯髒炸彈，是一個讓歐美談之色變的詞。是一種放射性散布裝置，利用放射性物質與常規炸藥相結合的放射性武器。髒彈與核武器或核彈並不相似。核彈所造成的，是威力比髒彈還要強大數以百萬倍的爆炸，且核彈的輻射雲可能會蔓延數十到數百平方英里，而髒彈的輻射影響範圍，可能只分布在距離爆炸地幾個街區或英里而已"},{"pid":"6217dbb846218a46b14ffb1688b390c8c9b77224","tid":220454,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T06:03:02.000Z","msg":"一個最簡易的髒彈甚至只需要把放射性物質放在那裡任其散播輻射，而不需具有爆炸性。<br />\n<br />\n大多數的髒彈並不會釋放出足以致人於死，直接導致嚴重疾病的輻射。但根據情況不同，髒彈爆炸可能會造成大眾恐懼和驚慌、污染財產，需要龐大的清理費用來善後。利用髒彈來造成污染和焦慮，常常是恐怖分子的主要目標。<br />\n<br />\n國際原子能機構 (IAEA)總幹事本月7日前往菲律賓參加原子能會議時<br />\n<br />\n呼籲各國警惕恐怖分子獲得放射性物質，從而得以製造髒彈。總幹事表示，核安全是長期存在的嚴峻問題，對恐怖分子可能取得核原料的所有國家都是真實的威脅。他指出，一旦核原料落入恐怖分子之手，後者就可以用其製造髒彈，因其製造方法遠比原子彈簡單。"},{"pid":"eed94127f6791a868fa92adeae4c5febdc1f2e4a","tid":220454,"uid":55732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T06:10:39.000Z","msg":"500萬？<br />\n西瓜核定蘋果核呀？"},{"pid":"90470213690e0fbe1b54d14e84b338f256998e7c","tid":220454,"uid":50728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T06:17:08.000Z","msg":"唔知點解睇到個topic覺得好好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4882dfd40e134f4ab06f0b6a50f8131644563079","tid":220454,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T06:18:40.000Z","msg":"你射到一粒出嚟  當你贏  <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0edaca3b85f0d1079d226c36eb27fde13ee638e5","tid":220454,"uid":19557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T06:24:51.000Z","msg":"有能力整500萬粒核彈就唔駛窮到咁喇 d 人民"},{"pid":"2fb54a38da5b9037bbdffde28b33b3f7b2143557","tid":220454,"uid":3716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T06:26:39.000Z","msg":"咀炮都打撚死人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7de2a7ccfa4ac0d7f7b09703f603ea83006ebab0","tid":220454,"uid":41262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T06:42:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>如果一次過射500萬 粒<br />\n<br />\n美國 即係滅國 是真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過問題是1粒 都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你跟邊個學廣東話架</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdf44ec15f8e2469fa322a89f